{"tid":1404696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汽車停放示威區域。即使非騷亂仍不獲賠償","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:03:04.000Z","uid":5195,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1529d71544184f3b9269760eda8d427276abfff","tid":1404696,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"對於已購買全保的車主，若汽車停放於示威區域，而於活動期間受到損壞，汽車保險又會作出賠償嗎？由於大部分車保均將「戰爭、侵略、外敵行動、敵對行為或軍事行動（無論有否宣戰）、內戰、叛變、軍事起義、起義、叛亂、革命、軍事或篡奪力量、戒嚴；具備民眾起義特質或構成民眾起義的民眾騷亂」列入不保事項，因此即使示威活動不被定性為「暴動」，保險公司亦可以「民眾騷亂」等原因拒絕賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bab6b0b138d8d04c2824de2d41ce56ee225ac2f","tid":1404696,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16aad521f4269d8ad0f77015fd1a331ddeeb4162","tid":1404696,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e544adc22edd509380c2853cfc60590cb2509c6","tid":1404696,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"無得賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893806d70a2fc7a975f81f2393bc84daa69af369","tid":1404696,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"叫鄉紳籌錢賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71886679c42a88d294f34a9de3a3ddd90de560a","tid":1404696,"uid":56439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"Sorry囉"},{"pid":"40eb62b7bad60d27657acac14f8717e2969a74ed","tid":1404696,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:59:23.00